name: PRIVATE SUITE! Onboard Japan Airlines Newest First Class
description:
For your chance to win First Class plane tickets (worth up
to $20,000!) for your next big trip and support a great cause, enter at https://omaze.com/trektrendy 

Today I’m flying onboard Japan Airlines (or JAL) First Class on my way to Tokyo. This flight is operated by their 777-300 and features their newest First Class Suites. With ticket prices at around $10,000 each way this is not your normal kind of flight! 

I’m starting my journey though in Las Vegas, so have to reposition to LAX to take my flight. This also means you guys will get to see onboard American Airlines A321 First Class… spoiler… it’s not great!

Follow my travel live : will.luxurytravel
